      <title>The best time to become a pet heifer was 10 years ago, the second best time is today.</title>
      <author> ForeverEgg </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1801498/the-best-time-to-become-a-pet-heifer-was--years-ago-the-second-best-time-is-today/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1801498-the-best-time-to-become-a-pet-heifer-was--years-ago-the-second-best-time-is-today/chapter/1801579/#comments</comments>
