      <title>Lost in The Country</title>
      <author> Thai_spice </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1791253/lost-in-the-country/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1791253-lost-in-the-country/chapter/1791296/#comments</comments>
