t;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Hey, you take bets on how long it takes me to do one of your stupid puzzles.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“They’re not stupid, you’re just not smart enough to solve them,” Morgan said defensively.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“But I am smart enough to realize your trans before you did.” The S-tier villain said with a smirk that made their already glowing yellow eyes light up just a bit brighter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Morgan pursed her lips. Okay, she had to admit looking back it was pretty obvious that she was trans. It really shouldn’t be a surprise that others would be able to figure it out. Sometimes Morgan was pretty oblivious to things that were right in front of her. “Okay fine… Wait, my family doesn’t know, do they?” She couldn’t imagine what they would do about her being trans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Chad knows. I don’t think anyone else does though. I think Chad even has a feminine sidekick outfit ready and waiting for you.” Alex paused before snapping their fingers. “He doesn’t anymore.” Alex thought for a minute. “On second thought,” they snapped again, and a spandex outfit with a miniskirt and a very open chest suddenly appeared on the couch, “It might make a funny Halloween outfit. Or maybe use it to trick your family if you want.” There was a part of Alex that envisioned a fun roleplay scenario that could be had, if Morgan ever fucking realized they were in love with her.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Morgan looked at the outfit and cringed. Really? Red, white, and blue spandex and thigh high boots? What was Chad even thinking… Okay maybe Morgan was a little morbidly curious as to what it would feel like to wear. “Okay, that’s… Wait, is my voice different?!” Morgan grabbed her throat. It felt smaller. Not only that but her Adam's apple was gone, and her voice was no longer low and gruff. “Did you already…” Morgan looked down at her body and found her clothes no longer fit her but hung off of her loose and baggy. Well all, except the shirt, which was now a little strained against a large pair of breasts. “You didn’t even snap!”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“I don’t need to snap,” Alex shrugged. “I like that people feel I actually have to do something to make my powers work if I snap instead of it being free wiiiillllll! Oh, fuck what are you doing?!” Alex covered their eyes and turned away as Morgan stripped off her top.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;“Gods, why did you make them this big?” She looked down at her naked chest. She had boobs. She had boobs! She suddenly felt like she was about to cry, but she pushed that aside in order to grab her tits. They felt so good in her hands, and she couldn't help but give them a hard squeeze that made her tingle all over, and especially in one area between her legs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Morgan finally looked back up and found Alex looking away, with their face and ears flaring a bright red. “Why are you looking away? You made these, and you even have tits sometimes.” Morgan couldn’t help but find it a bit funny that Alex was reacting like this, as she continued to squeeze and play with her new assets. Fuck, her nipples were really sensitive, so much that she had to bite her lip not to make a noise. “And aren’t you ‘I’m Mixx demisexual so nudity doesn’t faze me at all because I’m not madly in love with them’?” Morgan chuckled.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight:400"&gt;Alex felt like their feet were glued to the ground as their hand still covered their eyes. Part of them was tempted just to gouge out their eyes so that they couldn’t see. They would grow back eventually of course. 